<!-- About -->
<div class="bg-white py-5" id="about">
    <div class="container py-4">
        <div class="row align-items-center g-5">
            <div class="col-lg-4 text-center d-none d-lg-block">
                <span class="display-1 fw-bold text-primary opacity-25" style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 12rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em;">JM</span>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <p class="text-primary text-uppercase fw-bold small mb-2">About Me</p>
                <h2 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-4">IT Web Programmer</h2>
                <p class="text-muted fs-5 mb-3">
                    I'm a second-year IT Web Programming student at NSCC,
                    building a strong foundation in full-stack development and always eager to expand what I know.
                </p>
                <p class="text-muted fs-5 mb-3">
                    I'm driven by curiosity, like learning new frameworks, working through tricky problems,
                    or improving how I write code. I enjoy taking an idea and turning it into something real.
                </p>
                <p class="text-muted fs-5 mb-0">
                    Outside of coding, I'm usually playing games — everything from fast-paced FPS games to story-driven
                    adventures and indie games. Gaming is how I unwind and stay inspired, and it's a big part of what keeps me balanced.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

